Tamora Pierce Quotes quiz
[INS::INS]
Fun Trivia

How well do you know your Tamora Pierce books? Let's see! I'll give you a quote, and you tell me who said it. Enjoy!

Average score for this quiz is 7 / 10. Difficulty: Average. Played 2,250 times. As of Nov 28 17.
1. Alanna: The First Adventure.
"Ah. 'Free time.' I've heard about that. Don't fool yourself, Fire-Top. What with the extra hours of lessons for punishments,
and the work you get everyday, free time is an illusion. It's what you get when you die and the gods reward you for a life
working from dawn until midnight. We all face up to it sooner or later."

( ) Alex
( ) Raoul
( ) Gary
( ) Jonathon


